These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta, soy-milk, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, fishing, reading, skydiving
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking sprite and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
3. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking sprite##7
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | milk       | fanta | sprite        |
| Hobby      | reading  | fishing | skydiving        | collecting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, turtle, goldfish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, handball, skiing, baseball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere between the person who's sport is skiing and the owner of the turtle##7
2. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
3. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is baseball##5
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is handball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | turtle | ferret       | goldfish         | cat     |
| Sport   | handball   | baseball | skiing | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, musical, horror, drama
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, reggae, salsa, punk
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the fan of punk##1
2. the fan of punk is somewhere between the fan of reggae and the fan of d&b##7
3. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the fan of d&b is somewhere between the fan of punk and the person watching musical movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | drama | horror | family  |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | d&b  | punk   | reggae |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, singing, dancing, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, rugby, parkour, baseball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's hobby is puzzles##7
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | singing | hiking | puzzles       | dancing |
| Sport   | rugby      | lacrosse   | parkour | baseball  |

