.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, singing, woodworking, sudoku
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, canadian, polish, turkish
1. the turkish is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
2. the pakistani is somewhere to the left of the canadian##5
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the turkish is somewhere between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is writing##7
5. the turkish is on the left of the polish##1
6. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | writing   | sudoku | singing |
| Nationality   | pakistani      | canadian | turkish      | polish |

