.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, fanta, juice
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, polish, british, russian
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the british##1
2. the british is the person drinking juice##1
3. the polish is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the russian##3
6. the russian is somewhere between the mexican and the polish##7
7. the british is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | milk      | fanta | juice     |
| Nationality   | mexican    | russian | polish   | british |

