.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, cabbage, grapes, plum
There are 4 different nationalities: american, indian, turkish, mexican
1. the american is on the far left##1
2. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the indian##1
3. the person eating plum is on the far left or far right##3
4. the mexican is somewhere between the person eating papaya and the person eating grapes##7
5. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapes##5
6. the mexican is on the left or right of the turkish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | plum    | papaya   | cabbage | grapes  |
| Nationality   | american | turkish | mexican    | indian |

