.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, german, italian, polish
4 different pets are kept: goat, mouse, bird, goldfish
1. the german is not the owner of the goldfish##6
2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
3. the polish is the owner of the bird##1
4. the italian is somewhere between the polish and the indonesian##7
5. the german is on the left of the indonesian##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
7. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | polish | italian | german | indonesian |
| Pet           | bird   | goldfish    | goat       | mouse  |

