2. the person watching time-travel movies is not the owner of the bird##6
3. the owner of the goldfish is not the person watching animation movies##6
4. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
5. the person watching drama movies is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | zombie | time-travel | animation |
| Pet           | rabbit    | goldfish   | guinea-pig  | bird      |

