.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, crime, spy, adventure
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, country, techno, funk
1. the fan of funk is somewhere to the right of the fan of pop##5
2. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of pop##1
3. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
5. the person watching family movies is between the person watching crime movies and the fan of country##2
6. the fan of techno is somewhere between the fan of country and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | family | crime | spy   |
| Music-Genre   | country    | techno      | pop      | funk |

