1. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##6
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is handball##5
6. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is gardening##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | gardening | baking | photography | rock-climbing |
| Sport   | ice-hockey  | baseball    | handball    | soccer  |

