.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, skydiving, magic-tricks, rock-climbing
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, scooter, roller, boat
1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the roller is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the person driving the scooter##6
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
6. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person driving the airplane and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | rock-climbing | gardening | skydiving | magic-tricks |
| Transport   | airplane   | boat      | scooter        | roller  |

