.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, lemonade, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, dubstep, jazz, blues
1. the fan of dubstep is in an even position##4
2. the fan of blues is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the fan of jazz##7
3. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
4. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
7. the person drinking tea is the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | lemonade | tea | iced-tea   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | jazz   | blues | dubstep |

