.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, turtle, mouse, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, van, skateboard, subway
1. the owner of the mouse is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the owner of the turtle##7
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | turtle    | mouse | rat     | horse |
| Transport   | skateboard | subway  | van | tram |

 